"{\"uid\": \"kwqc.com-2024-07-12-free-summer-olympics-opening-ceremony-watch-party-families-impacted-by-cancer\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"DAVENPORT, Iowa (KWQC) - Families impacted by cancer are being invited to watch the Summer Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KWQC-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KWQC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KWQC-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KWQC-TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cancer Support Community Iowa & NW Illinois at Gilda's Club is hosting an opening ceremony watch party for any families impacted by cancer.\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to a media release, the watch party includes family-friendly competitions, a free lunch, and a livestream of the opening ceremony in Paris.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999780331691308, \"rank\": 2.196731337054179e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will be at 11:30 a.m. to 1:30 p.m. on July 26 at 1351 W. Central Park Ave., Suite 200, Davenport.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an all-ages event, with teens and kids welcome to bring a friend.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Registration for the event is required, and space is limited.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more details and to reserve a spot call 563-326-7504, emailprogram@gildasclub.org, or sign up onlinehere.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 KWQC.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": []}]}"